\begin_inset Formula $t_{w}(p/2^{n})$
\end_inset 

 will be a finite polynomial in 
\begin_inset Formula $w.$
\end_inset 

 By contrast, 
\begin_inset Formula \[
t_{w}\left(\frac{1}{3}\right)=\frac{2}{3(1-w)}\]

\end_inset 

